as Kuzmickas]]|LTU}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Pommel Horse}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Pommel Horse}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Nile Wilson]]|GBR}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Antonios Tantalidis]]|GRE}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Valentin Starikov]]|RUS}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Still Rings}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Still Rings}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Nile Wilson]]|GBR}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Paul Degouy]]|FRA}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Ivan Stretovich]]|RUS}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Vault}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Vault}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Kirill Popatov]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Valentin Starikov]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Viktar Hrankouski]]|BLR}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Parallel Bars}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Parallel Bars}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Ivan Stretovich]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Brinn Bevan]]|GBR}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Ahmet Onder]]|TUR}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Horizontal Bar}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Horizontal Bar}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Carlo Macchini]]|ITA}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Valentin Starikov]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Tin Srbic]]|CRO}}\n|- bgcolor=\"DFDFDF\"\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\"| '''Girls'''\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Team}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Team 2}}\n| {{Flagcountry|RUS}}\n| {{Flagcountry|GBR}}\n| {{Flagcountry|ROU}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|All-Around}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#All-Around 2}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Maria Kharenkova]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Kim Janas]]|GER}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Tyesha Mattis]]|GBR}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Vault}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Vault 2}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Ellie Downie]]|GBR}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Laura Jurca]]|ROU}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Tyesha Mattis]]|GBR}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Uneven Bars}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Uneven Bars}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Martina Rizzelli]]|ITA}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Louise Vanhille]]|FRA}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Tea Ugrin]]|ITA}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Balance Beam}}<br />{{DetailsLink|#Balance Beam}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Maria Bondareva]]|RUS}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Eythora Thorsdottir]]|NED}}\n| {{Flagathlete|[[Claire Martin (gymnast)|Claire Martin]]|FRA}}<br />{{Flagathlete|[[Andreea Iridon]]|ROU}}\n|-\n| {{nowrap|Floor Exer